            <thetext>If qx.test.bom.Blocker.testBlockElement is run *after* qx.test.bom.Blocker.testUnblockWholeDocument, it fails: The blocker element is expected to be as wide as the element it blocks (500px), but qx.bom.element.Dimension.getWidth returns 0. The blocker element&#39;s style.width attribute is set to &quot;500px&quot;, however.

